            <sortOrder>4</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If any of the catalog items or other topics are not able to classify the utterance then strictly ask if the incident needs to be created. If the user confirms then only run the employee incident creation action.</description>
